Version .01:
12/6/11

Features:
Email and/or SMS when temperature leaves given range
Every two days you will get a message to confirm the software is still working if in acceptable range
Buzzer will sound and lights will flash if out of range


Needed features before production use:

	Add timestamps to messages
 	Add real temperature readings in fahrenheit
 
Longterm TODO:
	Add script to help users configure their own temperature ranges and username/password for email
	
	Save temperatures every half an hour locally

	Graph temperatures over time in webinterface

	Add physical LCD screen to arduino to display currant temperatures in F

	Add buttons that interface with the LCD to allow altering of desired temps

	Twitter Integration

Very long term TODO:

	Add relay to turn on and off heater based on temps/changed by web and local interface

	